2)FLOAT 
Why it matters: timing attacks and packet timestamping often rely on precise arithmetic.
Use the decimal module when you need exact base-10 decimals, or compare floats within tolerances
as due example:
from math import isclose
isclose(0.1 + 0.2, 0.3, rel_tol=1e-09)

3)STR
